				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">What's the technique for using this thing? I wouldn't think equipping it when a fights going badly would be very dependable</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
Its more for getting out of zones/places where you need a TL to get out, or perhaps would have a very long run back to PoK. Classic examples would be PoFear or PoHate, Sebilis, the VoTS camp in Ssra, or leaving Chardok (or worse still, Chardok B). And unlike a gate potion it costs nothing to use and doesn't run out of charges. Obviously the downside is you need something to hit (e.g. a mob, /duel a friend, or summon an eye) and its unreliable for timing
<br />
</span></td>
