				<td colspan="2"><span>You guys are making this out to be too difficult.  He is a pretty MR bastard, but I did this quest long ago in my late 40's I believe.  I pulled him out, that was the worst part, had an add or 2 I chanted down.  and then let him chase me out in the open while I tried to land a charm.  Sure most of the charms were resisted but I had a full bar of mana and one did land before I was oom, after that I turned in my jade.  So if you're 50+ I don't think there is a real need to have anyone else help you do this, if you want to get it by factioning and farming go for it, or if you have a DE illusion mask or potion and have good enough faction to start with do that too, that's probably the easiest way.  If you opt for the charming route, yes he is MR, but you really don't need to waste someone elses time to debuff him imo.
